495
00:25:45,410 --> 00:25:47,145
YEAH.

496
00:25:51,149 --> 00:25:53,285
I'M STILL IN SHOCK.

497
00:25:53,285 --> 00:25:56,388
WE GOT A 12 SHARE.

498
00:25:56,388 --> 00:25:58,990
THAT'S DOUBLE WHAT
THE CLASSICAL FORMAT GOT

499
00:25:58,990 --> 00:26:00,358
ON ITS BEST NIGHT.

500
00:26:00,358 --> 00:26:03,295
AMAZING. FROM BEETHOVEN
