I DON'T KNOW.

510
00:26:20,879 --> 00:26:23,915
SUCCESS, YOU KNOW.
TO BE HAPPY.

511
00:26:23,915 --> 00:26:26,451
YOU WANT A COUPLE
OF BEAUTIFUL HOMES,

512
00:26:26,451 --> 00:26:28,920
