535
00:27:23,975 --> 00:27:26,945
WE'D ALL LOVE TO HAVE
EVERY BEAUTIFUL WOMAN WE SEE.

536
00:27:26,945 --> 00:27:28,913
AM I RIGHT?

537
00:27:28,913 --> 00:27:30,415
AND YOU CAN, JON.

538
00:27:30,415 --> 00:27:33,885
BECAUSE OF ME, YOU'RE
GOING TO BE FAMOUS.

539
00:27:33,885 --> 00:27:37,455
BECAUSE OF ME, YOU'RE
GOING TO MAKE MONEY.

540
00:27:39,624 --> 00:27:43,294
NOW, WHAT WOULD YOU DO
WITH HER

541
00:27:43,294 --> 00:27:47,399
