ON YOUR BED?

542
00:27:47,399 --> 00:27:49,034
MMM.

543
00:27:49,034 --> 00:27:51,536
WHAT WOULD YOU DO
WITH HER, JON?

544
00:27:51,536 --> 00:27:54,506
OKAY, OKAY.
I'M NOT A SAINT.

545
00:27:54,506 --> 00:27:56,374
HONESTY, JON.
THANK YOU.

546
00:27:56,374 --> 00:27:59,678
WE'D ALL LOVE TO HAVE
A WOMAN GUYS GO CRAZY OVER,

547
00:27:59,678 --> 00:28:01,413
A CAR THAT TURNS HEADS.

548
00:28:01,413 --> 00:28:03,782
EVERYBODY HAS FANTASIZED
ABOUT BEING FAMOUS.

549
00:28:03,782 --> 00:28:07,786
PEOPLE RECOGNIZING YOU,
BEGGING YOU FOR YOUR AUTOGRAPH.

550
00:28:07,786 --> 00:28:12,057
BUT MOST OF ALL, JON,
YOU'D LIKE TO HAVE POWER.

551
00:28:12,057 --> 00:28:14,793
REAL POWER.

552
00:28:14,793 --> 00:28:18,163
POWER TO DO
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

553
00:28:18,163 --> 00:28:19,431
YEAH.

554
00:28:19,431 --> 00:28:21,499
SEE? I SPEAK THE TRUTH.

555
00:28:21,499 --> 00:28:23,635
I KNOW WHAT PEOPLE WANT.

556
00:28:23,635 --> 00:28:25,970
THAT'S WHY THE SHOW WORKS.

557
00:28:25,970 --> 00:28:29,040
I KNOW WHAT YOU WANT.
THAT'S WHY WE WORK.

558
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:33,044
IF YOU STICK WITH ME,
YOU'RE GOING TO HIT THE ROOF.

559
00:28:33,044 --> 00:28:35,714
WE'LL GO THROUGH
THE STRATOSPHERE.

560
00:28:35,714 --> 00:28:39,250
