THROUGH THICK AND THIN.

561
00:28:40,351 --> 00:28:41,653
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

562
00:28:44,355 --> 00:28:47,726
WE'RE GOING TO HAVE SOME
WILD TIMES UP AHEAD, JON.

563
00:28:47,726 --> 00:28:50,261
