DID I GET YOU THERE?

958
00:46:33,590 --> 00:46:35,592
YOU DID,
BUT WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT

959
00:46:35,592 --> 00:46:37,928
MY STAYING ON YOUR SHOW
FOR AN HOUR?

960
00:46:37,928 --> 00:46:40,430
I TOLD YOU I WANTED
TO BE ON MY OWN.

961
00:46:40,430 --> 00:46:44,134
JON, I NEED YOU ON MY SHOW
JUST A LITTLE BIT LONGER.

962
00:46:44,134 --> 00:46:46,003
THAT'S NOT WHAT
WE TALKED ABOUT.

963
00:46:46,003 --> 00:46:49,006
I THINK I'M MISSING SOMETHING
HERE, LIKE A LITTLE GRATITUDE.

964
00:46:49,006 --> 00:46:52,509
LOOK, I WANT TO RIDE THIS BABY
JUST A LITTLE BIT LONGER

965
00:46:52,509 --> 00:46:55,179
AND MAKE SURE THE SHOW'S
IN A SOLID POSITION.

966
00:46:55,179 --> 00:46:57,181
IS THAT TOO MUCH TO ASK?

967
00:46:57,181 --> 00:46:59,783
ALL RIGHT.
THEN I'M ON MY OWN?

968
00:46:59,783 --> 00:47:01,318
YES, JON.

969
00:47:04,655 --> 00:47:06,790
ALL RIGHT, THEN.

970
00:47:06,790 --> 00:47:08,792
