YOU LEFT AT HER PLACE ANYTIME,

997
00:51:26,383 --> 00:51:28,885
PREFERABLY AT NIGHT,
WHEN YOU CAN TUCK HER IN.

998
00:51:28,885 --> 00:51:31,054
SHARON, SHE'S JUST
PLAYING WITH YOU.

999
00:51:31,054 --> 00:51:33,623
IS SHE THE FIRST,
OR HAVE THERE BEEN OTHERS?

1000
00:51:33,623 --> 00:51:36,726
SHE'S PROBABLY A FAN.
I DON'T KNOW.

1001
00:51:36,726 --> 00:51:38,095
YOU KNOW WHAT, JON?

1002
00:51:38,095 --> 00:51:40,964
DON'T LIE TO ME,
BECAUSE I AM NOT AN IDIOT.

1003
00:51:40,964 --> 00:51:44,034
I CAN SMELL HER
ALL OVER YOU.

1004
00:51:46,069 --> 00:51:48,738
