1014
00:52:11,895 --> 00:52:13,230
IT'S THAT YOU'VE CHANGED.

1015
00:52:13,230 --> 00:52:16,133
YOU SOLD YOURSELF OUT
TO GET WHAT YOU WANTED.

1016
00:52:16,133 --> 00:52:19,402
MAYBE IT TOOK THIS OTHER WOMAN
TO MAKE ME SEE IT.

1017
00:52:19,402 --> 00:52:20,904
I DON'T KNOW.

1018
00:52:20,904 --> 00:52:22,672
I'M OUT OF HERE.

1019
00:52:22,672 --> 00:52:25,008
OKAY, FINE.
I'M NOT GOING TO STOP YOU.

1020
00:52:25,008 --> 00:52:28,512
YOU WANT TO END IT THIS WAY,
THEN GO, LEAVE.

1021
00:52:28,512 --> 00:52:31,081
I DON'T NEED YOU, SHARON!

1022
00:52:58,475 --> 00:53:01,044
I AM SUCH AN IDIOT.

1023
00:53:05,115 --> 00:53:08,151
