1026
00:53:12,155 --> 00:53:14,491
THAT'S RIGHT, KARLIN.
I DIDN'T APPRECIATE IT.

1027
00:53:14,491 --> 00:53:15,792
NEITHER DID SHARON.

1028
00:53:15,792 --> 00:53:18,361
I DIDN'T KNOW YOU WERE STILL
SEEING EACH OTHER.

1029
00:53:18,361 --> 00:53:19,663
YEAH, RIGHT. NOT ANYMORE.

1030
00:53:19,663 --> 00:53:21,831
You can have any woman
you want now.

1031
00:53:21,831 --> 00:53:25,402
