OF THE GUY WHO CALLED UP,

1059
00:55:15,645 --> 00:55:19,149
THE ONE WHO CLAIMED TO KILL
THE WOMAN HE PICKED UP?

1060
00:55:19,149 --> 00:55:21,151
YOU THINK
HE'LL CALL BACK?

1061
00:55:21,151 --> 00:55:22,819
HE SAID HE WOULD.

1062
00:55:22,819 --> 00:55:26,156
MAYBE IT WAS JUST
A CRANK CALL.

1063
00:55:26,156 --> 00:55:28,158
