HE MIGHT CALL BACK AGAIN.

1066
00:55:36,666 --> 00:55:40,670
ARE YOU TELLING ME THAT
THERE REALLY WAS A MURDER?

1067
00:55:40,670 --> 00:55:41,838
YEAH, JON.

1068
00:55:41,838 --> 00:55:43,306
THE GUY WAS FOR REAL.

1069
00:55:43,306 --> 00:55:44,941
YOU SEEM SURPRISED.

1070
00:55:44,941 --> 00:55:48,311
