THREE MONTHS AGO.

1074
00:55:57,320 --> 00:55:59,522
VIVIAN PORTER'S HER NAME.

1075
00:55:59,522 --> 00:56:03,326
SHE WAS PUSHED OFF
A WAREHOUSE FIRE ESCAPE,

1076
00:56:03,326 --> 00:56:06,329
JUST LIKE
THE CALLER DESCRIBED.

1077
00:56:06,329 --> 00:56:09,332
SEVEN STORIES,
STRAIGHT DOWN.

1078
00:56:09,332 --> 00:56:11,334
OH...

1079
00:56:11,334 --> 00:56:13,403
GOD.

1080
00:56:15,972 --> 00:56:17,474
OH, JESUS.

1081
00:56:17,474 --> 00:56:19,976
WE DON'T HAVE A MOTIVE YET.

1082
00:56:19,976 --> 00:56:21,344
NOT A STRONG ONE, ANYWAY.

1083
00:56:21,344 --> 00:56:24,280
WE FIGURE IT'S PRETTY MUCH
WHAT HE SAID IT WAS --

1084
00:56:24,280 --> 00:56:25,815
A ONE-NIGHT STAND GONE BAD.

1085
00:56:25,815 --> 00:56:29,652
AND NOW HE'S GETTING HIS ROCKS
OFF CALLING YOUR SHOW

1086
00:56:29,652 --> 00:56:31,488
TELLING THE WORLD
WHAT HE DID.

1087
00:56:31,488 --> 00:56:34,491
JON, I'M GOING TO BE
DIRECT WITH YOU.

1088
00:56:34,491 --> 00:56:38,995
WE BROUGHT YOU DOWN HERE
TO ASK YOU ONE SIMPLE QUESTION.

1089
00:56:38,995 --> 00:56:41,431
YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THE CALLER?

1090
00:56:41,431 --> 00:56:44,934
LIKE WHO HE IS,
FOR EXAMPLE?

1091
00:56:44,934 --> 00:56:47,537
NO.

1092
00:56:47,537 --> 00:56:48,738
ARE YOU SURE?

1093
00:56:50,373 --> 00:56:52,942
YEAH, I'M POSITIVE.

1094
00:56:57,380 --> 00:56:59,716
YEAH, THAT'S WHAT WE FIGURED.

1095
00:57:01,785 --> 00:57:04,053
WE'RE GOING TO TALK TO
YOUR PARTNER, KARLIN PICKETT.

1096
00:57:04,053 --> 00:57:06,189
SEE WHAT HE KNOWS.

1097
00:57:06,189 --> 00:57:09,225
