YOU KEEP HIM TALKING, OKAY?

1104
00:57:24,574 --> 00:57:26,709
OKAY.

1105
00:57:27,744 --> 00:57:29,212
WE HAVE NOTHING MORE.

1106
00:57:30,914 --> 00:57:32,749
THANKS FOR YOUR TIME, JON.

1107
00:57:32,749 --> 00:57:34,250
OKAY, THANKS.

1108
00:57:34,250 --> 00:57:36,419
HEY, THIS IS
OUR PHONE NUMBER

1109
00:57:36,419 --> 00:57:39,422
