REALLY KILLED A WOMAN.

1119
00:58:01,177 --> 00:58:02,111
ARE YOU KIDDING?

1120
00:58:02,111 --> 00:58:03,313
NO, I'M NOT.

1121
00:58:03,313 --> 00:58:06,149
IT ALL HAPPENED EXACTLY
THE WAY HE DESCRIBED IT.

1122
00:58:07,617 --> 00:58:10,153
YOU DIDN'T TELL THEM
ANYTHING, DID YOU?

1123
00:58:10,153 --> 00:58:12,489
NO, I WANTED TO
TALK TO YOU FIRST.

1124
00:58:12,489 --> 00:58:15,158
WE GOT TO TELL THEM
WHO THIS GUY IS.

1125
00:58:15,158 --> 00:58:16,659
NO, WE CAN'T DO THAT.

1126
00:58:16,659 --> 00:58:17,660
WE HAVE TO.

1127
00:58:17,660 --> 00:58:18,928
NO, WE DON'T.

1128
00:58:18,928 --> 00:58:20,530
EDDIE --
EDDIE DIDN'T DO THIS.

1129
00:58:20,530 --> 00:58:22,098
EDDIE? EDDIE WHAT?

1130
00:58:22,098 --> 00:58:26,102
