WE GOT THE TOP-RATED SHOW.

1134
00:58:33,009 --> 00:58:34,511
THAT'S AN INCREDIBLE
ACCOMPLISHMENT.

1135
00:58:34,511 --> 00:58:38,114
YOU TELL THEM ABOUT EDDIE,
THEY'LL TAKE US OFF THE AIR.

1136
00:58:38,114 --> 00:58:40,149
SCREW THE SHOW.
THIS GUY KILLED A WOMAN.

1137
00:58:40,149 --> 00:58:41,551
HE DIDN'T KILL ANYBODY.

1138
00:58:41,551 --> 00:58:44,921
LET'S SAY BY SOME COINCIDENCE,
THEY TIE HIM TO A MURDER.

1139
00:58:44,921 --> 00:58:47,924
THE COPS WILL MAKE YOU AND ME
ACCOMPLICES TO IT.

1140
00:58:47,924 --> 00:58:50,026
