1144
00:58:56,165 --> 00:58:59,335
IF YOU WERE
TO PHONE THE COPS,

1145
00:58:59,335 --> 00:59:01,905
I WOULD FUCK YOU OVER
ROYALLY.

1146
00:59:01,905 --> 00:59:04,340
I AM NOT
SUFFERING THIS ALONE.

1147
00:59:04,340 --> 00:59:08,144
I'LL SAY YOU KNEW AS MUCH
