ABOUT VIVIAN, WAS I?

1185
01:01:59,382 --> 01:02:02,051
I REALLY PUSHED HER OFF
THAT BUILDING.

1186
01:02:02,051 --> 01:02:06,055
I'VE GOT TO GET THIS STUFF
OFF MY CHEST, YOU KNOW?

1187
01:02:06,055 --> 01:02:08,057
I MET ANOTHER WOMAN
LAST NIGHT.

1188
01:02:08,057 --> 01:02:11,360
I MEAN, I ACTUALLY LIKED HER,
YOU KNOW?

1189
01:02:11,360 --> 01:02:13,863
I DIDN'T WANT ANYTHING
TO HAPPEN TO HER,

1190
01:02:13,863 --> 01:02:16,866
BUT SHE STARTED TO LAUGH AT ME
WHEN WE DID IT.

1191
01:02:16,866 --> 01:02:19,368
I'M IN A GREAT DEAL OF PAIN
RIGHT NOW.

1192
01:02:19,368 --> 01:02:21,604
THIS WOMAN,
SHE WENT HOME WITH YOU?

1193
01:02:21,604 --> 01:02:24,107
YEAH -- NO, NO,
I WENT TO HER HOUSE.

1194
01:02:24,107 --> 01:02:26,109
IS SHE OKAY?

1195
01:02:26,109 --> 01:02:27,243
NO.

1196
01:02:27,243 --> 01:02:29,612
WHAT HAPPENED TO HER?

1197
01:02:29,612 --> 01:02:31,347
I KILLED HER...

1198
01:02:31,347 --> 01:02:33,282
WITH CYANIDE.

1199
01:02:33,282 --> 01:02:38,788
GET ME THE LOCATION
OF 555-7620.

1200
01:02:40,389 --> 01:02:42,892
OKAY, KEEP TALKING.
TELL US MORE ABOUT IT.

1201
01:02:42,892 --> 01:02:44,260
YOU KNOW HER NAME?

1202
01:02:44,260 --> 01:02:45,695
YEAH.

1203
01:02:45,695 --> 01:02:46,863
YEAH, WE'RE HERE.

1204
01:02:46,863 --> 01:02:49,532
WE GOT AN E.S.U.
AND SIX BLACK-AND-WHITES

1205
01:02:49,532 --> 01:02:51,534
HEADED FOR THE SOURCE
OF THE CALL.

1206
01:02:51,534 --> 01:02:53,536
UM, I'VE SAID TOO MUCH
ALREADY.

1207
01:02:53,536 --> 01:02:55,905
I...I REALLY...
I GOT TO GO.

1208
01:02:55,905 --> 01:02:57,907
Jon: NO, NO, NO,
TALK TO US.

1209
01:02:57,907 --> 01:02:59,242
COME ON,
WE'RE LISTENING.

1210
01:02:59,242 --> 01:03:01,744
I'LL CALL AGAIN.

1211
01:03:01,744 --> 01:03:03,746
[ DIAL TONE ]

1212
01:03:05,815 --> 01:03:07,717
DAMN IT.

1213
01:03:09,786 --> 01:03:11,287
WHAT IS GOING ON?

1214
01:03:11,287 --> 01:03:14,290
I DON'T KNOW. EDDIE CALLED
ON HIS OWN THIS TIME.

1215
01:03:14,290 --> 01:03:15,792
GET HIM TO STOP,
UNDERSTAND?

1216
01:03:15,792 --> 01:03:17,794
YOU CAN'T BUY P.R.
LIKE THIS.

1217
01:03:17,794 --> 01:03:20,296
I BET WE MAKE IT
TO THE NATIONAL NEWS.

1218
01:03:20,296 --> 01:03:22,298
I CAN'T DO THIS.
THIS IS INSANE.

1219
01:03:22,298 --> 01:03:24,467
WE GOT THE SYNDICATORS
BY THE BALLS.

1220
01:03:24,467 --> 01:03:25,968
IF EDDIE KEEPS CALLING,

1221
01:03:25,968 --> 01:03:28,971
THEY'LL BE BEGGING US
TO DO A NATIONWIDE SHOW.

1222
01:03:28,971 --> 01:03:31,741
NOW GET WITH THE PROGRAM.

1223
01:03:33,109 --> 01:03:34,443
Wilkinson: GENTLEMEN.

1224
01:03:34,443 --> 01:03:36,612
WE GOT AN ADDRESS,
BUT IT'S WRONG.

1225
01:03:36,612 --> 01:03:39,248
LOOKS LIKE HE'S GOT
A SCRAMBLER ON THE LINE.

1226
01:03:39,248 --> 01:03:41,951
AH, WHAT A DRAG.

1227
01:03:41,951 --> 01:03:43,419
YEAH, HE'S A SMART ONE.

1228
01:03:43,419 --> 01:03:46,055
CALLED IN TO HEADQUARTERS
AND GOT A CONFIRMATION.

1229
01:03:46,055 --> 01:03:47,223
ABOUT THE CALLER?

1230
01:03:47,223 --> 01:03:48,357
YEAH.

1231
01:03:48,357 --> 01:03:50,793
ANOTHER WOMAN WAS KILLED
LAST NIGHT.

1232
01:03:50,793 --> 01:03:52,795
THE CORONER'S
MAKING AN AUTOPSY NOW,

1233
01:03:52,795 --> 01:03:56,098
BUT THE CALLER PROBABLY KILLED
HER THE WAY HE DESCRIBED.

1234
01:03:56,098 --> 01:03:57,600
CYANIDE POISONING THIS TIME.

1235
01:03:57,600 --> 01:03:59,635
THE STUFF'S
EASY ENOUGH TO GET,

1236
01:03:59,635 --> 01:04:01,771
AND YOU CAN MIX IT
WITH ANYTHING.

1237
01:04:01,771 --> 01:04:03,005
YOU'D NEVER KNOW.

1238
01:04:03,005 --> 01:04:05,708
EXCEPT THAT IT SMELLS
LIKE BURNT ALMONDS.

1239
01:04:05,708 --> 01:04:07,109
JESUS.

1240
01:04:07,109 --> 01:04:08,611
THAT'S TWO IN A ROW.

1241
01:04:08,611 --> 01:04:11,614
LOOKS LIKE YOU GOT YOURSELVES
A GENUINE SERIAL KILLER

1242
01:04:11,614 --> 01:04:13,616
CALLING IN TO YOUR SHOW.

1243
01:04:13,616 --> 01:04:15,618
WE GOT TO GET DOWNTOWN.
YOU READY?

1244
01:04:15,618 --> 01:04:16,786
YEAH.

1245
01:04:16,786 --> 01:04:18,688
THANKS, GUYS.

1246
01:04:18,688 --> 01:04:20,189
Wilkinson: YOU TRIED.

1247
01:04:20,189 --> 01:04:22,258
WE'LL KEEP MONITORING.

1248
01:04:26,996 --> 01:04:28,998
THIS GUY'S REALLY
KILLING PEOPLE.

1249
01:04:28,998 --> 01:04:32,001
I HAD NO IDEA THAT IT WOULD
GO THIS FAR, MAN.

1250
01:04:32,001 --> 01:04:34,003
YOU'RE IN ON THIS,
AREN'T YOU?

1251
01:04:34,003 --> 01:04:36,505
WHO THE HELL
DO YOU THINK YOU ARE?

1252
01:04:36,505 --> 01:04:39,508
THIS IS A TOTAL FUCKING
SURPRISE TO ME, JON.

1253
01:04:39,508 --> 01:04:41,510
LOOK, I KNEW EDDIE
WAS WHACKED,

1254
01:04:41,510 --> 01:04:43,846
BUT NEVER LIKE THIS.

1255
01:04:43,846 --> 01:04:45,848
THIS SCARES ME.

1256
01:04:45,848 --> 01:04:48,517
I GOT TO TELL YOU
SOMETHING.

1257
01:04:48,517 --> 01:04:50,519
EDDIE OWED ME A FAVOR.

1258
01:04:50,519 --> 01:04:53,022
I SAVED HIS ASS
FROM A LOAN SHARK ONCE,

1259
01:04:53,022 --> 01:04:56,359
BUT I HAD NO IDEA THIS ASSHOLE
MIGHT BE KILLING WOMEN.

1260
01:04:56,359 --> 01:04:58,361
WELL, THAT'S IT.
I'M TELLING THE COPS.

1261
01:04:58,361 --> 01:04:59,795
YOU CAN'T.

1262
01:04:59,795 --> 01:05:03,199
EDDIE MIGHT KILL US IF HE
THINKS WE WENT TO THE COPS.

1263
01:05:03,199 --> 01:05:06,202
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?
LET HIM KEEP KILLING WOMEN?

1264
01:05:06,202 --> 01:05:07,270
JON...

1265
01:05:09,038 --> 01:05:12,541
YOU LET ME HANDLE THIS
MY OWN WAY, YOU UNDERSTAND?

1266
01:05:12,541 --> 01:05:15,544
COPS ARE FUCKING IDIOTS.
THEY WOULDN'T BE COPS.

1267
01:05:15,544 --> 01:05:17,546
YOU DON'T TELL THEM NOTHING.

1268
01:05:17,546 --> 01:05:20,049
NOW, I'LL GO TO EDDIE.

1269
01:05:20,049 --> 01:05:22,551
I'LL GET HIM TO STOP.

1270
01:05:22,551 --> 01:05:25,621
YOU LET ME DO IT
MY OWN WAY.

1271
01:05:55,084 --> 01:05:56,619
HEY.

1272
01:05:58,054 --> 01:06:00,256
TOUGH DAY, HUH?

1273
01:06:01,924 --> 01:06:03,659
YEAH.

1274
01:06:03,659 --> 01:06:06,362
IT'S ALWAYS DARKEST
BEFORE THE DAWN.

1275
01:06:06,362 --> 01:06:08,431
THAT'S WHAT I ALWAYS SAY.

1276
01:06:21,610 --> 01:06:24,146
JESUS, I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

1277
01:06:24,146 --> 01:06:25,748
HE KILLED HER.

1278
01:06:25,748 --> 01:06:28,751
THIS BASTARD'S FOLLOWING ME.

1279
01:06:28,751 --> 01:06:32,455
CAN I SPEAK WITH
DETECTIVE WILKINSON, PLEASE?

1280
01:06:32,455 --> 01:06:34,090
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

1281
01:06:34,090 --> 01:06:36,092
YOU'VE GOT A CALL
ON LINE THREE.

1282
01:06:36,092 --> 01:06:37,526
I CAN'T TAKE IT.

1283
01:06:37,526 --> 01:06:39,261
HE SAYS IT'S IMPORTANT.

1284
01:06:39,261 --> 01:06:40,663
TAKE A MESSAGE.

1285
01:06:40,663 --> 01:06:43,966
HE SAID TO TELL YOU
EDDIE'S ON THE PHONE.

1286
01:06:43,966 --> 01:06:45,134
WHICH LINE?

1287
01:06:45,134 --> 01:06:46,369
THREE.

1288
01:06:48,971 --> 01:06:50,139
HELLO?

1289
01:06:50,139 --> 01:06:53,142
I finally get to
speak to you in person.

1290
01:06:53,142 --> 01:06:54,143
Hello?

1291
01:06:54,143 --> 01:06:55,578
YEAH, I'M HERE.

1292
01:06:55,578 --> 01:06:58,314
I really liked talking
to you on the radio.

1293
01:06:58,314 --> 01:06:59,815
It made me feel better.

1294
01:06:59,815 --> 01:07:02,318
I left a little souvenir
in your apartment.

1295
01:07:02,318 --> 01:07:03,486
Remember Cynthia?

1296
01:07:03,486 --> 01:07:04,987
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

1297
01:07:04,987 --> 01:07:07,990
If I were you, I'd go home
before the police do.

1298
01:07:07,990 --> 01:07:09,992
They might
get the wrong idea

1299
01:07:09,992 --> 01:07:12,328
when they find Cynthia's
wallet and clothing

1300
01:07:12,328 --> 01:07:14,330
not so well hidden
in your bedroom.

1301
01:07:14,330 --> 01:07:15,564
[ CLICK ]

1302
01:07:19,168 --> 01:07:22,171
[ SIREN ]

1303
01:07:22,171 --> 01:07:25,541
[ HELICOPTER WHIRRING ]

1304
01:07:28,477 --> 01:07:29,912
SIR, WE JUST BAGGED THIS.

1305
01:07:29,912 --> 01:07:31,981
YOU MIGHT WANT TO
TAKE A LOOK.

1306
01:07:50,199 --> 01:07:51,534
BETSY, IT'S JON.

1307
01:07:51,534 --> 01:07:54,203
WHERE'S KARLIN?
I GOT TO TALK TO HIM.

1308
01:07:54,203 --> 01:07:55,371
I don't know.

1309
01:07:55,371 --> 01:07:57,873
WE'VE BEEN TRYING TO
GET AHOLD OF HIM.

1310
01:07:57,873 --> 01:07:58,874
Ah, Christ.

1311
01:07:58,874 --> 01:08:00,109
THE COPS WERE HERE.

1312
01:08:00,109 --> 01:08:02,111
THERE'S A WARRANT OUT
FOR YOUR ARREST.

1313
01:08:02,111 --> 01:08:05,114
I don't understand
what's going on here, Jon.

1314
01:08:05,114 --> 01:08:07,683
I'M BEING FRAMED
FOR A MURDER.

1315
01:08:08,717 --> 01:08:11,053
WELL, YOU'RE
IN A PILE OF SHIT.

1316
01:08:11,053 --> 01:08:13,122
THANKS. I KNOW.

1317
01:08:16,892 --> 01:08:18,894
I'VE GOT TO GO.

1318
01:08:18,894 --> 01:08:21,230
Wait, hold on, Jon.

1319
01:08:39,248 --> 01:08:41,317
[ DING DONG ]

1320
01:08:43,752 --> 01:08:45,321
KARLIN!

1321
01:08:48,257 --> 01:08:50,326
KARLIN!

1322
01:10:03,499 --> 01:10:05,868
EDDIE.

1323
01:10:05,868 --> 01:10:08,470
EDDIE, EDDIE, EDDIE,
WHERE ARE YOU?

1324
01:10:08,470 --> 01:10:11,173
HERE YOU ARE.

1325
01:10:26,255 --> 01:10:27,590
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

1326
01:10:27,590 --> 01:10:28,591
ENGINEERING.

1327
01:10:28,591 --> 01:10:29,592
Roger.

1328
01:10:29,592 --> 01:10:31,594
JON,
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

1329
01:10:31,594 --> 01:10:34,029
EVERYBODY'S LOOKING
FOR YOU.

1330
01:10:34,029 --> 01:10:36,565
ROGER, I WANT YOU
TO DO ME A FAVOR.

1331
01:10:36,565 --> 01:10:38,367
SURE,
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

1332
01:10:38,367 --> 01:10:40,302
I WANT YOU
TO TAKE AN ADDRESS

1333
01:10:40,302 --> 01:10:41,837
THAT'S NEAR THE STATION.

1334
01:10:41,837 --> 01:10:44,340
I want you to meet me
at that gas station.

1335
01:10:44,340 --> 01:10:46,742
I need you to bring
a few things.

1336
01:10:46,742 --> 01:10:48,110
WHAT KIND OF THINGS?

1337
01:11:55,110 --> 01:11:58,113
EDDIE?

1338
01:12:04,453 --> 01:12:07,456
EDDIE?

1339
01:12:27,776 --> 01:12:29,778
JON?

1340
01:12:29,778 --> 01:12:33,315
KARLIN.

1341
01:12:33,315 --> 01:12:35,484
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

1342
01:12:35,484 --> 01:12:40,289
I CAME TO HAVE A LITTLE
CONVERSATION WITH EDDIE.

1343
01:12:40,289 --> 01:12:44,960
I WANTED TO FIND OUT
WHAT THE HELL IS GOING ON.

1344
01:12:44,960 --> 01:12:48,030
YEAH. I GUESS WE BOTH
HAVE SOMETHING

1345
01:12:48,030 --> 01:12:49,865
TO TALK TO HIM ABOUT.

1346
01:12:49,865 --> 01:12:51,333
IS THAT MY GUN?

1347
01:12:51,333 --> 01:12:53,702
YEAH.

1348
01:12:53,702 --> 01:12:55,704
YOU GOT BALLS, JON.

1349
01:12:55,704 --> 01:12:58,340
I DON'T HAVE
MUCH OF A CHOICE.

1350
01:12:58,340 --> 01:13:01,176
YOU KNOW EDDIE KILLED
ANOTHER WOMAN LAST NIGHT?

1351
01:13:01,176 --> 01:13:02,745
CYNTHIA.

1352
01:13:02,745 --> 01:13:04,046
THE WOMAN
FROM THE NIGHTCLUB

1353
01:13:04,046 --> 01:13:05,848
THAT WANTED
TO GO HOME WITH YOU?

1354
01:13:05,848 --> 01:13:10,252
YEP. HE PLANTED HER CLOTHING
AND HER WALLET IN MY HOUSE.

1355
01:13:10,252 --> 01:13:12,988
THE POLICE
THINK I KILLED HER.

1356
01:13:12,988 --> 01:13:14,990
THERE'S A WARRANT
OUR FOR MY ARREST.

1357
01:13:14,990 --> 01:13:16,692
EDDIE. GODDAMN IT.

1358
01:13:16,692 --> 01:13:19,261
WE'RE GOING TO HAVE
TO TAKE HIM TO THE COPS.

1359
01:13:19,261 --> 01:13:20,963
YEAH, WE DO.

1360
01:13:20,963 --> 01:13:24,366
I DON'T KNOW
WHERE HE IS.

1361
01:13:28,704 --> 01:13:32,040
WHILE WE'RE WAITING,
DO YOU WANT A DRINK?

1362
01:13:32,040 --> 01:13:34,376
SURE.
WHAT HAS HE GOT?

1363
01:13:34,376 --> 01:13:36,445
LET ME LOOK.

1364
01:13:40,115 --> 01:13:43,552
HE'S GOT SOME BOURBON,
OKAY?

1365
01:13:43,552 --> 01:13:44,553
YEAH. WHATEVER.

1366
01:13:44,553 --> 01:13:46,555
ALL RIGHT.

1367
01:14:02,037 --> 01:14:04,039
HERE YOU GO,
LITTLE BROTHER.

1368
01:14:04,039 --> 01:14:06,375
DOES HE HAVE ANY ICE?

1369
01:14:06,375 --> 01:14:09,411
WHY DON'T YOU GO LOOK?

1370
01:14:12,247 --> 01:14:14,950
IT'S A WILD PLACE, HUH?

1371
01:14:21,390 --> 01:14:26,695
HE'S BEEN A SQUATTER HERE
EVER SINCE I MET HIM.

1372
01:14:29,264 --> 01:14:32,668
I'M REALLY GLAD
YOU'RE HERE, JON.

1373
01:14:32,668 --> 01:14:33,869
OH, YEAH?

1374
01:14:33,869 --> 01:14:37,606
ACTUALLY, I THOUGHT
YOU MIGHT BE KIND OF PISSED.

1375
01:14:37,606 --> 01:14:39,074
PLEASE.

1376
01:14:39,074 --> 01:14:41,076
DRINK OKAY?

1377
01:14:41,076 --> 01:14:43,946
YEAH.

1378
01:14:43,946 --> 01:14:45,247
BY THE WAY,

1379
01:14:45,247 --> 01:14:49,518
THERE'S SOMETHING
I WANT TO CONFESS TO YOU.

1380
01:14:49,518 --> 01:14:53,288
THAT IS THAT, UH,
THERE IS NO EDDIE.

1381
01:14:53,288 --> 01:14:55,624
I MEAN...

1382
01:14:55,624 --> 01:14:57,960
I'M EDDIE.

1383
01:15:00,028 --> 01:15:02,764
SEE,
WITH THIS EQUIPMENT HERE,

1384
01:15:02,764 --> 01:15:06,301
THIS IS A SOUND PROCESSOR
AND A SYNTHESIZER.

1385
01:15:06,301 --> 01:15:09,037
I CHANGE THE MAKEUP
OF MY VOICE.

1386
01:15:09,037 --> 01:15:10,506
I BECAME EDDIE.

1387
01:15:10,506 --> 01:15:13,475
OH, MY GOD.

1388
01:15:13,475 --> 01:15:17,479
YEAH. I GOT ALL
THE REGULAR SUPPLIES.

1389
01:15:17,479 --> 01:15:20,015
SEE, HERE'S THE SCRAMBLER,

1390
01:15:20,015 --> 01:15:22,985
FOR THROWING OFF
THE POLICE TRACING DEVICES,

1391
01:15:22,985 --> 01:15:24,486
AND A DIALING MECHANISM.

1392
01:15:24,486 --> 01:15:27,489
I PRERECORDED EDDIE'S VOICE
ON THIS TAPE MACHINE,

1393
01:15:27,489 --> 01:15:33,128
AND I SENT IT TO OUR SHOW
BY WAY OF THIS AUTOMATIC TIMER.

1394
01:15:33,128 --> 01:15:35,564
ALL I HAD TO DO

1395
01:15:35,564 --> 01:15:36,965
WAS STICK TO A SCRIPT.

1396
01:15:36,965 --> 01:15:39,034
I MADE IT SOUND
REAL AUTHENTIC,

1397
01:15:39,034 --> 01:15:41,236
EVEN FOOLED YOU,
LITTLE BROTHER.

1398
01:15:44,673 --> 01:15:47,476
OH. AH.

1399
01:15:47,476 --> 01:15:49,177
WHAT'S THE MATTER, JON?

1400
01:15:49,177 --> 01:15:53,181
I FEEL A LITTLE DIZZY.

1401
01:15:53,181 --> 01:15:57,486
VIVIAN AND CYNTHIA --
GOD, THEY WERE HOT,

1402
01:15:57,486 --> 01:15:59,454
ESPECIALLY VIVIAN.

1403
01:15:59,454 --> 01:16:02,824
I KILLED THEM BOTH,
YOU KNOW.

1404
01:16:02,824 --> 01:16:06,562
[ RETCHING NOISES ]

1405
01:16:06,562 --> 01:16:08,597
I DIDN'T MEAN
TO KILL VIVIAN.

1406
01:16:08,597 --> 01:16:11,433
WE WERE GETTING IT ON
ONE NIGHT ON THE RAILING

1407
01:16:11,433 --> 01:16:16,371
OF THIS FIRE ESCAPE.
OH, GOD. SHE WAS SWEET.

1408
01:16:16,371 --> 01:16:18,540
ANYWAY,
WE JUST GOTTEN THROUGH

1409
01:16:18,540 --> 01:16:21,176
AND SHE STARTS
TO MEALY-MOUTH ALL THIS,

1410
01:16:21,176 --> 01:16:23,078
"I WANT TO SEE
YOU AGAIN,"

1411
01:16:23,078 --> 01:16:24,713
YOU KNOW,
RELATIONSHIP JARGON.

1412
01:16:24,713 --> 01:16:27,249
I SUPPOSE SHE DIDN'T LIKE
MY RESPONSE

1413
01:16:27,249 --> 01:16:30,018
BECAUSE SHE GOES
TO SLAP ME, I STEP BACK,

1414
01:16:30,018 --> 01:16:32,955
THE BITCH GOES OVER
THE SIDE OF THE FIRE ESCAPE

1415
01:16:32,955 --> 01:16:37,893
AND FALLS SEVEN STORIES
TO THE CONCRETE. SMACK.

1416
01:16:37,893 --> 01:16:42,397
IT FREAKED ME OUT,

1417
01:16:42,397 --> 01:16:45,334
BUT THAT'S
WHEN I DECIDED

1418
01:16:45,334 --> 01:16:49,004
I WOULD USE HER DEATH
TO HELP ME.

1419
01:16:49,004 --> 01:16:54,409
I WOULD INVENT A KILLER
WHO WOULD CALL INTO OUR SHOW

1420
01:16:54,409 --> 01:16:57,579
